longBusinessSummary: International Personal Finance plc, together with its subsidiaries, provides consumer credit in Europe and Mexico. The company offers credit products, such as online payment transaction; revolving credit line; microbusiness loans; digital installment loans; credit card; hybrid loans; and home credit installment loans, as well as medical and life insurances. International Personal Finance plc was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Leeds, the United Kingdom.
